Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:10.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:38.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta visited Nean, the town where \NRebecca and her siblings lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:43.77,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but it turned out to be where Gauche's \Nbeloved little sister Marie lived, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:46.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Are you read—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.35,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:49.99,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her this instant, you trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:54.11,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That night, a certain incident struck Nean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:03.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Snow? When did it pile up so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even the season for that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.46,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you two think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:16.09,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:24.81,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:26.99,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,you're all my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.79,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Pursuit Over the Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:04.51,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Luca, Marco, where could \Nyou have gone at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.58,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Barshim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.65,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Helen, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:10.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they didn't just go out to pee—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you marry my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.94,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more important \Nthan Marie, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.47,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the heck's going on in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:32.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it snowing this time \Nof year? This is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:39.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just happened to be in the area.\NIt's just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.38,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of my Magic Knight buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And Noelle, this is my friend Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.45,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.58,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Buddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.26,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.71,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:58.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a whole bunch of kids go \Nup to the mountains earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:02.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have some \Nfestival this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.72,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,That must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make you bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.38,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The old Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:15.35,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I feel magical power in this snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.98,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,There is magic at work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.48,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that can control others...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.63,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,and that only affects children \Nwhose magic hasn't matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.74,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.12,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,A number of ours were taken, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:30.21,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean to do, \Ntaking all these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.75,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old hag, what do you mean, "taken"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.75,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Marie was, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.47,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, that is what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:39.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:40.42,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Theresa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.54,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,How could you let that happen,\Nyou stupid old hag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.72,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:49.33,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,So quick to resort to violence... \NYou really are a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.02,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hit me, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:55.33,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But that won't bring back the children.\NIt won't bring back Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.27,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:02.38,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't feel better until I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:06.78,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on now, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just cool down a little, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:23.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Knight needs to \Nstay calm at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.63,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:30.07,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Calm, eh? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.70,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll calmly kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I went too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you stupid little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:41.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! \NNow's not the time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find some clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:46.35,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What? As if it'll be that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.86,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The magic mirror that I have Marie \Nkeep with her at all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.61,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to transmit \Nto it because of this snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:58.12,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but if I search for the \Nmana in that mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.26,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to figure out where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:06.10,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I may have figured\Nthat out, but I'm still killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.38,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you while giving thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:12.89,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, as well. I'm going to get the \Nkids from the church and the town back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:16.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Old Sister, leave this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.78,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No. As much as it pains me to \Nsay it, this old hag will be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's not just an ordinary old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:27.11,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose to \Nyou young'uns just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:33.08,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Marco's an idiot and Luca's too\Nheadstrong, so I'm worried about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:37.00,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? If something \Nwere to happen to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! I'll get them \Nback, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:49.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They'll laugh at you if you're \Nall panicky when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.18,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fly on your own either, can you? \NDo you want to dangle, like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:08.95,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,The town might be attacked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.78,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind staying behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And could you report back \Nto the Magic Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.06,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.04,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stay behind with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.49,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I made so many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.91,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's all get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.66,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:59.08,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the church. What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:03.08,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems out of it. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.86,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:08.28,top,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you stay good boys and \Ngirls with the spell I'm using.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.31,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Did he put a spell on everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:15.03,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Brother did say that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:18.55,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,the mirror he gave me would \Nprotect me from magic a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.60,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on to this mirror as if it were me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.46,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:28.05,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my spell on you has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:31.32,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why. You bad little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:37.32,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be friends if you won't be \Na good girl and stay under my spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:42.49,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,But you're wrong. Putting someone under \Na spell and making them do what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:45.12,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't make them a real friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.98,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.13,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,A friend would never say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.76,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Neige...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.55,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to damage the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:07.60,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.60,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Baro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:16.69,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,She's the prize this time. Imagine\Nhaving that much magic at her age!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:22.01,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Having this many brats means a big payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.21,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,That brat barely has any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:31.35,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to only bring ones \Nwith a lot of magic, Neige!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:32.75,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Baro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.80,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Just gonna have to throw \Ntrash like this away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:48.65,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. Stop wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:54.11,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Let's draw the magic out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.41,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We're close. The mana's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:13.29,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,These enemies must possess \Npowerful magic. Be on your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.84,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:17.88,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please be safe, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:33.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please stay calm. \NWe, the Magic Knights, will find all the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:36.11,main,Guy b,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:39.06,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Please get my son back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.67,main,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.11,main,Pim,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Luca and Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.24,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Asta and Gauche \Nwill bring them all back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:50.05,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! So don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:50.87,main,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.38,main,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Why's our house broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:57.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupidsta and Gauche will fix \Nthat when they get back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:00.19,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,We should do what we can \Nto fix it up for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:02.59,main,Pim,0000,0000,0000,,There's snow everywhere inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:06.64,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I need to contact \Nthe other Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:13.55,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights' Headquarters here, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I seen you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you really from headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:25.07,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! It's not my main job, but \NCaptain Jack ordered me to help out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:29.87,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing so good lately that they're \Nletting me take a break from all the battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.70,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.67,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's snow! There's snow in Nean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.67,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Snow? How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:43.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Someone made this snow fall \Non the town using magic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:45.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,so they could kidnap all the kids here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:48.68,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,What? You should hurry up and \Ncontact the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm doing right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.01,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.69,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry \Nabout anymore! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I'm even more worried now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.87,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I sense mana in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:14.37,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,A cave. That must be where \Nall the abducted children are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:20.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche, could you let me down a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.47,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem. I don't care \Nabout anyone besides Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go, then jump off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:39.61,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! How can you call \Nyourself a Magic Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:46.87,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to the others, \Nas long as I can protect Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:55.08,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,On the day that I, a former prisoner,\Njoined the Black Bulls, the captain told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:59.21,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You can just protect whoever \Nyou want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.22,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly what I'll be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:04.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.47,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:11.12,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful. He's covered in \Nwounds, and he's frostbitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.22,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:16.59,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. He's under a spell\Nand still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:21.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right... Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.11,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:33.30,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asta... Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:38.27,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now? He erased the magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.30,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.41,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.87,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Recovery Magic: Sacred Healing Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.89,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:56.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, old lady! \NYou can even heal wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:58.34,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.40,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:03.94,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's so hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:04.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go save your \Nsister and the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wait in that cave by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.82,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No! I'm scared, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:17.91,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NYou're a man, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once, I'll let you \Nborrow my Black Bulls robe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have this on, you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:32.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's got Magic Knight \Ncourage in it, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:37.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can wait until we get back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.19,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But don't forget! I'm only \Nletting you borrow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to give it back to me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:46.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You'll give it back, right? \NAnd don't get any snot on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.74,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:51.87,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we have to hurry. \NI'm worried about the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.43,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a damn maze in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:03.21,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But the mana's getting stronger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.46,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little longer, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.97,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good. More, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:20.66,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to squeeze every last\Ndrop of magic out of you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.97,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,And done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:29.24,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Are we going \Nto use our prize next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:34.98,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.11,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.98,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,You can't defy Baro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:46.79,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up. I'm gonna make \Na fortune off of your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.26,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:53.89,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.14,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:02.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Marie, you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:10.97,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's an enemy, Baro! He has\Na Magic Knight robe on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:14.68,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! How'd they find us so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.93,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Do something! Use your magic, Neige!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.16,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.16,main,Neight,0000,0000,0000,,Snow Magic: Snow Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.25,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Mirror Shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.26,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck is that spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.70,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't hit him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:42.48,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hurry up and use a \Ndifferent spell, you oaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:48.75,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,S-Snow Creation Magic: Snow Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:56.23,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:05.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:10.37,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating one or two won't make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:14.68,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Neige can keep creating an \Ninfinite number of these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:15.55,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.02,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Reflect Refrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.88,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,All of my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:48.38,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's too strong. And he's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:52.27,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... This isn't what we were told about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.97,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I only accepted this job\Nbecause we were told that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.30,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,it'd just be draining brats of their magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.30,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with this guy's magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.90,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Baro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.87,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:10.81,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Think! There has to be some way! Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:23.62,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Move an inch, and see what happens to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:28.07,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.24,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:33.09,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,if I get annoyed and put a little \Ntoo much strength into my grip?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:39.34,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Neige, beat him to a pulp—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:49.50,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.40,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.92,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.77,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:15.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.18,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! How dare you \Nthrow something so dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What if it had hit Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:24.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait. This was to save Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:28.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what if {\i1}you{\i0} had hit Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.73,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd ever hit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.31,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My love for Marie is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.48,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.73,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:39.77,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:44.70,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,These children have had their \Nmagic sucked out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:50.71,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,If left like this, they may never \Nbe able to use magic again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Their magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:57.66,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That man was saying how it'd \Nbe worth a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:02.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.93,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. This is not good. Not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:06.93,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Baro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.89,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,We had enough on our hands \Nwith that monster of a guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.19,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,but now that his friends have\Nshown up, we don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.71,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,This boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:26.48,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? He doesn't \Nhave any magic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:30.11,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! I've never \Nseen trash like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:32.33,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I take a closer look,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:35.46,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,you're just some peon that doesn't \Neven have a Magic Knight's robe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:39.38,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Neige, you take care of \Nthat sister complex freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.46,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:45.05,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just have to take \Ncare of this peon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,forgive you!
