Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:38.67,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:42.88,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Staying Behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:41.61,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Staying Behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:47.17,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Luca... Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:51.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. I'm sure Asta and the \Nothers will bring them back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:57.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we do a quiz to lighten the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:58.66,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:04.86,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Where is Asta from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:07.69,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hage Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:09.03,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:10.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:12.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How old is Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:15.45,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:20.69,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Then when is Asta's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:22.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,October 4th.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:24.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What is Asta's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:29.42,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming the Wizard King someday... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:33.22,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:37.15,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:41.10,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:44.69,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't hear you. Ready, and... bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:47.21,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I get to be the star again!
